      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELECTRA OPAL (6) was out of the placings last time when eighth at this track (16.91) but scored five back at this track (16.50). Solid record here at the distance winning eight races. Can atone. WALTZING BRUTE (5) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (16.72). Has a good record here at this journey. The form out of his last race has been franked. Cannot be taken lightly. GLAMOROUS JEWEL (4) struggled to get involved last start after settling off pace at this track, but prior to that won by half a length at this track (16.85) beating Dinosaur Deano in a Grade 5 on February 27. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. RIPPER RILEY (1) has hardly put a foot wrong of late and will be competitive again.",
